descriptionHtml:
‘Dare to be you’ — the MONA womenswear collection brings together style, quality, and a fabulous fit.

Enjoy exclusive rewards when you download the free MONA app.

With the free MONA app, you can shop our collection and access our services on the go. Download it now to shop safely and comfortably, find new fashion favourites, and enjoy exclusive discounts and rewards.

What to expect from the MONA app:
- A safe and secure shopping experience
- Fuss-free shopping, whenever you please
- Up-to-date information on special offers and discounts
- The latest trends and classic designs
- Your personal wishlist—perfect for saving your favourite fashion finds
- An easy-to-use search bar—enter the product name, number or category
- Outfit inspiration to help you create a new ensemble
- Easy access to your wishlist, orders and account
- Size guides to help you find your perfect fit

Find us on Pinterest
https://www.pinterest.co.uk/MONA_Fashion/

About us:
At MONA, we create clothing for confident, chic women who are young at heart. We like to get to know our customers, so you know that we understand your needs and can offer tailored, personal style advice for all your upcoming events.

Our mantra is ‘dare to be you’, and our stylish designs will help you to do just that. All our garments are crafted with care using the finest quality materials, with fastidious attention to detail—so you can look forward to looking your best with clothes that are designed and cut to fit, flatter and make you feel fabulous.

Enjoying the MONA app?
Please rate it on the Play Store or App Store.
